Fixed issue with closing the simulation.
Fixed issue with closing the simulation.

Added description for procedures and other stuff again. Added a warningbox when starting a procedure or script without capturing. Modified message box to allow **text** to be formatted as bold. Fixed new_scripting so that ProcedureArgs that consist of ProcedureArgs are correctly unpacked. Added examples for procedures for scripting.

commit_message: Added description for procedures and other stuff again. Added a warningbox when starting a procedure or script without capturing. Modified message box to allow **text** to be formatted as bold. Fixed new_scripting so that ProcedureArgs that consist of ProcedureArgs are correctly unpacked. Added examples for procedures for scripting.
Changed name of example procedue script and adjusted the args. Fixed local ramper

commit_message: Added crystal commands to protocol v1.0.0

Legacydevice works now. We need to add the code as a kwarg in send_message and send_and_wait_for_response, because I remove deduce command code from the legacyCommunicator and we need to prepend the code to the answer so that the device can correctly parse the answers. I also disabled get_overview currently because it has no commandcontract with a code yet and will therefore not work. But I dont think we need it anyway

commit_message: Legacydevice works now. We need to add the code as a kwarg in send_message and send_and_wait_for_response, because I remove deduce command code from the legacyCommunicator and we need to prepend the code to the answer so that the device can correctly parse the answers. I also disabled get_overview currently because it has no commandcontract with a code yet and will therefore not work. But I dont think we need it anyway
Fixed deduce command examples and other system tests
Fixed deduce command examples and other system tests
